---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Skief Labs" description="Built by someone who learned systems out of necessity. Learn about Skief Labs, founder Sardar Azimov, and our approach to B2B systems.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="heading-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-navy-900 mb-8">
          Built by someone who learned systems out of necessity.
        </h1>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          <p>Skief Labs exists because growing businesses are routinely held together by people doing work that systems should handle.</p>
          <p>Manual follow-ups. Copied data. Unclear ownership. Processes that sort of work — until growth breaks them.</p>
          <p>We've seen this pattern too many times to keep solving it one person at a time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR POINT OF VIEW -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-linen">
            Our point of view
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Most B2B companies don't stall because of bad strategy or bad people.</p>
          <p>They stall because their systems never evolved as the business did.</p>
          <p>As teams grow, tools multiply, data fragments, responsibility blurs, and humans quietly become the connective tissue holding everything together. That works — until it becomes fragile.</p>
          <p>Our work is about replacing that fragility with systems that operate reliably — whether or not anyone is watching.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE FOUNDER -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <p class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-blue-500 mb-4">The Founder</p>
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy-900 mb-2">
            Sardar Azimov
          </h2>
          <p class="text-navy-900/60 text-base">Founder & Principal</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Sardar's background is in business, marketing, and sales — not in engineering or computer science.</p>
          <p>He learned automation, AI, and systems design out of necessity: building ways to scale commercial output without endlessly hiring or burning teams out. That origin matters.</p>
          <p>It means every system Skief Labs designs starts with business questions, not technical ones:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-navy-900/70 pl-4">
            <li>Where is human effort being wasted on work that shouldn't require humans?</li>
            <li>Where is risk hiding inside a manual step?</li>
            <li>What should stay human — and why?</li>
            <li>What should never be automated?</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-semibold">Judgment comes before technology. Always.</p>
          <p>Sardar leads every Skief Labs engagement at the architecture level — ensuring solutions stay grounded in business reality rather than technical novelty.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW THE TEAM WORKS -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-linen mb-8">
          How the team works
        </h2>
        <p class="text-linen text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif italic mb-8">
          Skief Labs operates as a studio — deliberately small, deliberately senior.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>Projects are architected at a senior level and executed by trusted specialists in data engineering, automation, and AI systems. Every engagement is reviewed for clarity, stability, and ownership before it's delivered.</p>
          <p class="text-linen font-semibold">There are no junior handoffs. No hidden subcontracting. No black boxes.</p>
          <p>Clients always know who is responsible for what — and why decisions are being made.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-navy-900 mb-8">
          What makes us different
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-1 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg mb-8">
          <p>We are not an agency.</p>
          <p>We are not freelancers.</p>
          <p>We are not traditional consultants.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We build systems — two specific kinds — with deliberate restraint.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>We work on problems we're genuinely equipped to solve.</p>
          <p>We don't take on engagements to fill capacity.</p>
          <p>We say no when something shouldn't be built.</p>
          <p>We document everything so clients never need to come back for something they already paid for.</p>
          <p>We measure success by how little our clients need us over time — not by how much they do.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-navy-900 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mt-8 font-semibold">
          That last point is the most important one. Dependency is easy to create and profitable to maintain. We've chosen not to.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MENTORSHIP TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-linen mb-16 text-center">
        What people say about Sardar
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
          <div class="text-blue-500 text-3xl mb-4 font-serif">"</div>
          <p class="text-linen/80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Sardar is an expert in cold outreach, offering valuable assistance in strategy, next steps, and innovative ideas.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-linen/10 pt-4">
            <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-linen">Spyros Tsoukalas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
          <div class="text-blue-500 text-3xl mb-4 font-serif">"</div>
          <p class="text-linen/80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Sardar had plenty of amazing and actionable ideas for my challenge and explained his thinking and strategic insights patiently and thoroughly.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-linen/10 pt-4">
            <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-linen">Adrian Finzelberg</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-linen/10 rounded-lg p-8">
          <div class="text-blue-500 text-3xl mb-4 font-serif">"</div>
          <p class="text-linen/80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Sardar's experience runs deep. He shared so much high impact advice in our session. Super valuable, concise, and helpful!
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-linen/10 pt-4">
            <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-linen">Eben Meyer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
      <p class="text-navy-900/50 text-sm mt-3 italic">No pitch. No obligation. Just clarity.</p>
      <p class="text-navy-900/40 text-sm mt-8 italic font-serif">More business. Less busyness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
